      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "It has been a mistake to suppose\nthat the owner of the tall tower is\nalso complete director Of the city\nadministration. President J. M, r.\nRichardson and General Manager D..\nl.. Huntington are running the tall\ntower people a close race for the\ncity ownership.\n\n\nSaturday President Richardson and\nGeneral Manager Huntington of the\nWashington Water Power company\nasked the board of public works for\npermission to pave Howard street be-\ntween the car tracks with asphalt\nfrom Front avenue to Riverside ave.\nnue..\n\n\nThe board Of public works through\nSecretary ONO filed with the city\nclerk this afternoon a recommended\nton to the city council, which meets\ntomorrow night, that the permission\nbe granted."
    }
